{"id": "webh_specs", "modality": "web", "name": "Specs", "task": {"description": "Build a product comparison / spec-sheet page for 'Compare Phones' at 1920px wide comparing THREE phones side by side. A header row has an empty top-left cell then three equal-width phone columns, each with an image placeholder, model name, and price (Aero $799, Aero Pro $999, Aero Max $1199). Below, a dense specification table with a left attribute column and the three phone columns, at least 14 attribute rows (Display, Resolution, Chip, RAM, Storage, Rear camera, Front camera, Battery, Charging, Weight, Water resistance, Biometrics, Colors, OS) with a value in every cell. Alternating row shading. A sticky compare header keeps the phone names visible on scroll. Responsive: at 375px it shows one phone column at a time with a selector, or the table scrolls horizontally within its container.", "requirements": ["A header row aligns three equal-width phone columns over the spec table, each with image, name, and price", "The three prices appear exactly (Aero $799, Aero Pro $999, Aero Max $1199)", "The spec table has a left attribute column plus the three phone columns, all aligned", "There are at least 14 attribute rows with a value in every cell (no empty unaligned cells)", "Alternating rows are shaded consistently (repetition) and no cell text is clipped", "The phone-name header stays visible on scroll (sticky) and stays aligned to its columns", "On desktop nothing overflows horizontally; the table fits the page width", "At 375px the comparison remains usable (single-column selector or horizontally scrollable table within its container), not a squashed 4-column grid", "Column widths for the three phones are equal", "The price/header typography outranks the spec values (hierarchy)"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 66, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4843, "rv_n_defects": 18, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 24960}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 66, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4854, "rv_n_defects": 50, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 23795}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 4809, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 4609}], "ss_img": "images/web/webh_specs_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/web/webh_specs_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Compare Phones - Aero Series</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 60px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #2563eb;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile phone selector */\n        .phone-selector {\n            display: none;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .phone-selector select {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 15px 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            background: white;\n            color: #374151;\n        }\n\n        /* Comparison table container */\n        .comparison-container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .comparison-table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        /* Sticky header */\n        .sticky-header {\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 10;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .header-row {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .header-row th {\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .header-row th:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .empty-cell {\n            width: 25%;\n            background: transparent;\n        }\n\n        .phone-header {\n            width: 25%;\n        }\n\n        .phone-image {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 160px;\n            background: linear-gradient(145deg, #f1f5f9, #e2e8f0);\n            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            margin: 0 auto 20px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .phone-image::before {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 10px;\n            left: 50%;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 40px;\n            height: 6px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            border-radius: 3px;\n        }\n\n        .phone-name {\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .phone-price {\n            font-size: 1.2rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        /* Specification rows */\n        .spec-row {\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row:nth-child(even) {\n            background: #f9fafb;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row:nth-child(odd) {\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row td, .spec-row th {\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: left;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            border-right: 1px solid #f3f4f6;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row td:last-child, .spec-row th:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .spec-label {\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #374151;\n            background: #f8fafc !important;\n            width: 25%;\n        }\n\n        .spec-value {\n            color: #6b7280;\n            width: 25%;\n        }\n\n        /* Highlight differences */\n        .spec-row:hover {\n            background: #eff6ff !important;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row:hover .spec-label {\n            background: #dbeafe !important;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile styles */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 20px;\n            }\n\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n                margin-bottom: 30px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-selector {\n                display: block;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-container {\n                overflow-x: auto;\n                -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-table {\n                min-width: 800px;\n            }\n\n            .header-row th {\n                padding: 20px 15px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-image {\n                width: 80px;\n                height: 100px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-name {\n                font-size: 1.1rem;\n            }\n\n            .phone-price {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n            }\n\n            .spec-row td, .spec-row th {\n                padding: 15px 12px;\n                font-size: 0.9rem;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 15px;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-table {\n                min-width: 700px;\n            }\n\n            .header-row th {\n                padding: 15px 10px;\n            }\n\n            .spec-row td, .spec-row th {\n                padding: 12px 8px;\n                font-size: 0.85rem;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Compare Phones</h1>\n        \n        <div class=\"phone-selector\">\n            <select id=\"phoneSelect\">\n                <option value=\"all\">Compare All Phones</option>\n                <option value=\"aero\">Aero - $799</option>\n                <option value=\"aero-pro\">Aero Pro - $999</option>\n                <option value=\"aero-max\">Aero Max - $1199</option>\n            </select>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"comparison-container\">\n            <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n                <thead class=\"sticky-header\">\n                    <tr class=\"header-row\">\n                        <th class=\"empty-cell\"></th>\n                        <th class=\"phone-header\">\n                            <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-price\">$799</div>\n                        </th>\n                        <th class=\"phone-header\">\n                            <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero Pro</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-price\">$999</div>\n                        </th>\n                        <th class=\"phone-header\">\n                            <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero Max</div>\n                            <div class=\"phone-price\">$1199</div>\n                        </th>\n                    </tr>\n                </thead>\n                <tbody>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Display</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">6.1\" Super Retina XDR OLED</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">6.3\" Super Retina XDR OLED</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">6.7\" Super Retina XDR OLED</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Resolution</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">2556 \u00d7 1179 pixels<br>460 ppi</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">2796 \u00d7 1290 pixels<br>460 ppi</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">2796 \u00d7 1290 pixels<br>460 ppi</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Chip</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">A16 Bionic chip<br>6-core CPU</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">A17 Pro chip<br>6-core CPU</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">A17 Pro chip<br>6-core CPU</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">RAM</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">6GB</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">8GB</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">8GB</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Storage</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">128GB, 256GB, 512GB</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">128GB, 256GB, 512GB, 1TB</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">256GB, 512GB, 1TB</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Rear Camera</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Dual 48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Triple 48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide<br>12MP Telephoto (3x)</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Triple 48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide<br>12MP Telephoto (5x)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Front Camera</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Battery</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">3349 mAh<br>Up to 20 hours video</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">3274 mAh<br>Up to 23 hours video</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">4441 mAh<br>Up to 29 hours video</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Charging</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">20W wired<br>15W MagSafe wireless</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">27W wired<br>15W MagSafe wireless</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">27W wired<br>15W MagSafe wireless</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Weight</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">171g (6.02 oz)</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">187g (6.60 oz)</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">221g (7.80 oz)</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Water Resistance</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 minutes</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 minutes</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 minutes</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Biometrics</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Colors</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Pink, Yellow, Green,<br>Blue, Black</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Natural Titanium,<br>Blue Titanium,<br>White Titanium,<br>Black Titanium</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Natural Titanium,<br>Blue Titanium,<br>White Titanium,<br>Black Titanium</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">Operating System</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                        <th class=\"spec-label\">5G</th>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Sub-6GHz</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Sub-6GHz + mmWave</td>\n                        <td class=\"spec-value\">Sub-6GHz + mmWave</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </tbody>\n            </table>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Mobile phone selector functionality\n        document.getElementById('phoneSelect').addEventListener('change', function() {\n            const selectedPhone = this.value;\n            const table = document.querySelector('.comparison-table');\n            const headers = table.querySelectorAll('.phone-header');\n            const rows = table.querySelectorAll('.spec-row');\n\n            if (selectedPhone === 'all') {\n                // Show all columns\n                headers.forEach(header => header.style.display = 'table-cell');\n                rows.forEach(row => {\n                    const cells = row.querySelectorAll('td');\n                    cells.forEach(cell => cell.style.display = 'table-cell');\n                });\n            } else {\n                // Hide all phone columns first\n                headers.forEach((header, index) => {\n                    header.style.display = 'none';\n                });\n                \n                rows.forEach(row => {\n                    const cells = row.querySelectorAll('td');\n                    cells.forEach(cell => cell.style.display = 'none');\n                });\n\n                // Show selected phone column\n                let columnIndex;\n                switch(selectedPhone) {\n                    case 'aero': columnIndex = 0; break;\n                    case 'aero-pro': columnIndex = 1; break;\n                    case 'aero-max': columnIndex = 2; break;\n                }\n\n                headers[columnIndex].style.display = 'table-cell';\n                rows.forEach(row => {\n                    const cells = row.querySelectorAll('td');\n                    if (cells[columnIndex]) {\n                        cells[columnIndex].style.display = 'table-cell';\n                    }\n                });\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Compare Phones - Aero Series</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n            background: #f8fafc;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1920px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 40px 60px;\n        }\n\n        h1 {\n            font-size: 3rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            color: #0f172a;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 60px;\n            letter-spacing: -0.02em;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile phone selector */\n        .phone-selector {\n            display: none;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .phone-selector select {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 16px 20px;\n            font-size: 1.1rem;\n            border: 2px solid #e2e8f0;\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            background: white;\n            color: #1a1a1a;\n        }\n\n        /* Comparison table container */\n        .comparison-container {\n            background: white;\n            border-radius: 16px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .table-wrapper {\n            overflow-x: auto;\n        }\n\n        .comparison-table {\n            width: 100%;\n            border-collapse: collapse;\n            min-width: 800px;\n        }\n\n        /* Sticky header */\n        .sticky-header {\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 10;\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .header-row {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n        }\n\n        .header-row th {\n            padding: 0;\n            border: none;\n        }\n\n        .empty-cell {\n            width: 25%;\n            height: 80px;\n        }\n\n        .phone-header {\n            width: 25%;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n        }\n\n        .phone-image {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 120px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            border-radius: 12px;\n            margin: 0 auto 16px;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n            text-align: center;\n            line-height: 1.2;\n        }\n\n        .phone-name {\n            font-size: 1.5rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 8px;\n            letter-spacing: -0.01em;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n        }\n\n        .phone-price {\n            font-size: 1.3rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n        }\n\n        /* Specification rows */\n        .spec-row {\n            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row:nth-child(even) {\n            background: #f8fafc;\n        }\n\n        .spec-row:nth-child(odd) {\n            background: white;\n        }\n\n        .spec-label {\n            width: 25%;\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            color: #374151;\n            background: #f1f5f9;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n        }\n\n        .spec-value {\n            width: 25%;\n            padding: 20px 24px;\n            color: #1f2937;\n            border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0;\n            vertical-align: top;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n            hyphens: auto;\n        }\n\n        .spec-value:last-child {\n            border-right: none;\n        }\n\n        .highlight {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 4px 8px;\n            border-radius: 6px;\n            font-size: 0.9rem;\n            font-weight: 600;\n            display: inline-block;\n            word-wrap: break-word;\n            overflow-wrap: break-word;\n        }\n\n        /* Mobile styles */\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 20px;\n            }\n\n            h1 {\n                font-size: 2rem;\n                margin-bottom: 30px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-selector {\n                display: block;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-table {\n                min-width: 600px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-header {\n                padding: 20px 15px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-image {\n                width: 60px;\n                height: 90px;\n                font-size: 0.8rem;\n            }\n\n            .phone-name {\n                font-size: 1.2rem;\n            }\n\n            .phone-price {\n                font-size: 1.1rem;\n            }\n\n            .spec-label,\n            .spec-value {\n                padding: 16px 12px;\n                font-size: 0.9rem;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 375px) {\n            .container {\n                padding: 15px;\n                max-width: 375px;\n                overflow-x: hidden;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-container {\n                max-width: 100%;\n                overflow: hidden;\n            }\n\n            .table-wrapper {\n                border-radius: 16px;\n                max-width: 100%;\n                overflow-x: auto;\n            }\n\n            .comparison-table {\n                min-width: 360px;\n                max-width: none;\n            }\n\n            .phone-header {\n                padding: 15px 8px;\n                min-width: 90px;\n                max-width: 90px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-image {\n                width: 50px;\n                height: 75px;\n                font-size: 0.7rem;\n                margin-bottom: 8px;\n                padding: 2px;\n            }\n\n            .phone-name {\n                font-size: 1rem;\n                margin-bottom: 4px;\n                line-height: 1.1;\n            }\n\n            .phone-price {\n                font-size: 0.9rem;\n                line-height: 1.1;\n            }\n\n            .spec-label {\n                padding: 12px 8px;\n                font-size: 0.8rem;\n                min-width: 90px;\n                max-width: 90px;\n            }\n\n            .spec-value {\n                padding: 12px 8px;\n                font-size: 0.8rem;\n                line-height: 1.3;\n                min-width: 90px;\n                max-width: 90px;\n            }\n\n            .highlight {\n                font-size: 0.7rem;\n                padding: 2px 4px;\n                margin: 1px 0;\n                display: inline-block;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1>Compare Phones</h1>\n        \n        <div class=\"phone-selector\">\n            <select id=\"phoneSelect\">\n                <option value=\"all\">Compare All Models</option>\n                <option value=\"aero\">Aero</option>\n                <option value=\"aero-pro\">Aero Pro</option>\n                <option value=\"aero-max\">Aero Max</option>\n            </select>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"comparison-container\">\n            <div class=\"table-wrapper\">\n                <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n                    <thead class=\"sticky-header\">\n                        <tr class=\"header-row\">\n                            <th class=\"empty-cell\"></th>\n                            <th class=\"phone-header\" data-phone=\"aero\">\n                                <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-price\">$799</div>\n                            </th>\n                            <th class=\"phone-header\" data-phone=\"aero-pro\">\n                                <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero Pro</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-price\">$999</div>\n                            </th>\n                            <th class=\"phone-header\" data-phone=\"aero-max\">\n                                <div class=\"phone-image\">Phone Image</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-name\">Aero Max</div>\n                                <div class=\"phone-price\">$1,199</div>\n                            </th>\n                        </tr>\n                    </thead>\n                    <tbody>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Display</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">6.1\" OLED</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">6.3\" OLED <span class=\"highlight\">ProMotion</span></td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">6.7\" OLED <span class=\"highlight\">ProMotion</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Resolution</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">2556 \u00d7 1179</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">2622 \u00d7 1206</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">2796 \u00d7 1290</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Chip</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">A16 Bionic</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">A17 Pro</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">A17 Pro <span class=\"highlight\">Enhanced</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">RAM</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">6GB</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">8GB</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">12GB</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Storage</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">128GB, 256GB</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">256GB, 512GB</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">512GB, 1TB</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Rear Camera</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide<br>12MP Telephoto (3x)</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">48MP Main<br>12MP Ultra Wide<br>12MP Telephoto (5x)<br><span class=\"highlight\">LiDAR</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Front Camera</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">12MP TrueDepth <span class=\"highlight\">Enhanced</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Battery</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">3,279 mAh<br>Up to 20 hours video</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">3,650 mAh<br>Up to 23 hours video</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">4,422 mAh<br>Up to 29 hours video</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Charging</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">20W Wired<br>15W MagSafe<br>7.5W Qi</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">27W Wired<br>15W MagSafe<br>7.5W Qi</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">30W Wired<br>15W MagSafe<br>7.5W Qi<br><span class=\"highlight\">Reverse Wireless</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Weight</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">171g (6.03 oz)</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">187g (6.60 oz)</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">221g (7.80 oz)</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Water Resistance</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 min</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 min</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">IP68<br>6m for 30 min</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Biometrics</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID<br><span class=\"highlight\">Touch ID</span></td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Face ID<br><span class=\"highlight\">Touch ID</span></td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Colors</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Pink, Yellow, Green, Blue, Black</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Natural Titanium, Blue Titanium, White Titanium, Black Titanium</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">Natural Titanium, Blue Titanium, White Titanium, Black Titanium</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Operating System</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">iOS 17</td>\n                        </tr>\n                        <tr class=\"spec-row\">\n                            <td class=\"spec-label\">Connectivity</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">5G, Wi-Fi 6, Bluetooth 5.3</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">5G, Wi-Fi 6E, Bluetooth 5.3</td>\n                            <td class=\"spec-value\">5G, <span class=\"highlight\">Wi-Fi 7</span>, Bluetooth 5.3</td>\n                        </tr>\n                    </tbody>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Mobile phone selector functionality\n        const phoneSelect = document.getElementById('phoneSelect');\n        const phoneHeaders = document.querySelectorAll('.phone-header');\n        const specValues = document.querySelectorAll('.spec-value');\n\n        phoneSelect.addEventListener('change', function() {\n            const selectedPhone = this.value;\n            \n            if (selectedPhone === 'all') {\n                // Show all phones\n                phoneHeaders.forEach(header => header.style.display = 'table-cell');\n                specValues.forEach(value => value.style.display = 'table-cell');\n            } else {\n                // Hide all phones first\n                phoneHeaders.forEach(header => header.style.display = 'none');\n                specValues.forEach(value => value.style.display = 'none');\n                \n                // Show selected phone\n                const selectedHeader = document.querySelector(`[data-phone=\"${selectedPhone}\"]`);\n                if (selectedHeader) {\n                    selectedHeader.style.display = 'table-cell';\n                    \n                    // Show corresponding spec values\n                    const headerIndex = Array.from(phoneHeaders).indexOf(selectedHeader);\n                    const specRows = document.querySelectorAll('.spec-row');\n                    specRows.forEach(row => {\n                        const values = row.querySelectorAll('.spec-value');\n                        if (values[headerIndex]) {\n                            values[headerIndex].style.display = 'table-cell';\n                        }\n                    });\n                }\n            }\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}